# Where We Go From Here

Starting **Day 101**, we'll shift from learning Flutter basics to **making your app production-ready**.

The roadmap will include:

1. Push the complete project to GitHub.
2. Clean up the project structure.
3. Deploy the FastAPI backend on an AWS EC2 instance.
4. Set up PostgreSQL on AWS (instead of SQLite).
5. Configure Nginx and a custom domain.
6. Enable HTTPS with SSL.
7. Update the Flutter app to use the live backend instead of your local IP.
8. Prepare the app for release on the Google Play Store.

This next phase will turn your project into something that other people can actually use over the internet.
